The paper deals with learning-to-rank, which is a subfield of information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also discusses counterfactual inference techniques, which are commonly used in causal inference (cs.LG). The paper proposes a new method for optimizing ranking metrics using deep networks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI).
